Package agh.alleviation.model

Class Seance

java.lang.Object
agh.alleviation.model.EntityObject
agh.alleviation.model.Seance
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Externalizable, java.io.Serializable
@Entity
public class Seance
extends EntityObject
Class responsible for representation of a movie's seance. It keeps the information about the movie, the hall where seance takes place, the seance's date and its price. One movie can have many seance, but a seance can be assigned only to one movie. In one hall there can take place many seances, but a seance can be assigned only to one hall.
Author:
Ksenia Fiodarava
See Also:
Movie, Hall, Serialized Form
